detail.title: V2.2 Software Upgrade
detail.description:
Proposal to upgrade the blockchain to 'v2.2.0'. 
This upgrade includes the changes discussed to move community-pool funds to a vesting account as mentioned here: https://discord.com/channels/932715756423086090/936620266392526849/1161729169537900635. In order to bring the vesting schedule in accordance with tokenomics, we propose the following :
 	- Transfer Community Pool funds (i.e, 150,000,000 PASG) to a new multisig wallet controlled by team 
 	- The multisig wallet will be restricted so it can ONLY transfer funds to the Community Pool. 
 	- This multisig wallet will be NOT be able to complete any other types of transactions (AKA no staking, trading NFTs, voting, etc.) 
 	- Once vesting begins, the team will transfer funds back to the Community Pool in accordance with the schedule 
 This will not change anything on chain for the community or validators—it simply ensures vesting remains in line with the whitepaper. The upgrade also includes airdrop list for Town-1 and Town-2 users.

detail.title: Proposal to Allocate Foundry Funds to Apello
detail.description:
This proposal seeks to allocate 150,000 PASG tokens from the Passage Foundry to Apello. This will support the integration of Passage Chain into Apello, a toolkit for Cosmos-based projects and their communities.
As the primary platform for community discourse, members of the Passage Discord will benefit from Apello's chain-based roles, functionality, and tools including:
Roles for NFT owners in the Passage ecosystem (such as Strange Clan and MetaHuahua).
Roles for PASG token participants (e.g., token holders, stakers, and liquidity providers).
Token-gated channels for exclusive community discussions.
Seamless verification based on token ownership and traits.
NFT sales tracker bot.
Web app covering on-chain events like sales, listings, and bids.
Sales leaderboard highlighting top collections by volume and timeframe.

Passage Chain would join Juno, Terra, Stargaze, Teritori, and Injective as the sixth Cosmos chain integrated with Apello.
The Passage Foundry accounts for 120,000,000 PASG. This proposal requests less than 0.1% of Foundry funds to be allocated to Apello for the benefit of the Passage community. One of the Foundry's core aims is “fostering and supporting the creation of innovative and useful projects built on or in support of the Passage ecosystem,” and we believe Apello integration would directly align with this.

About Apello
Apello offers a comprehensive suite of free, open-source tools designed for Cosmos NFTs. 
It offers a wide range of features and functionality that enable communities to easily manage and track their NFT collections, such as token gating and sales tracking.

Project Website: https://www.apello.xyz/ 
Documentation: https://use.apello.xyz/apello/ 
Github: https://github.com/Apello-xyz/ 
Discord: https://discord.gg/apelloxyz

detail.title: ParamChange Proposal: Enable inflation
detail.description: This proposal is for enabling the inflation on Passage mainnet. This proposal proposes to set the min-inflation parameter to 8% and max-inflation parameter to 10%. We will review the inflation rewards and make updates every quarter to cross-verify and match with the inflation specified in the tokenomics.
